premise_source_doc_sentence: Throughout his career , Harris has also released several highly successful singles , including `` Bring Em Out '' , `` Whatever You Like '' , `` Live Your Life ''  (  featuring Rihanna  )  , `` Dead and Gone ''  (  featuring Justin Timberlake  )  , `` Ball ''  (  featuring Lil Wayne  )  and `` No Mediocre ''  (  featuring Iggy Azalea  )  .
